'''[http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Armageddon Armageddon]''' 

===Hyphenation===
Ar·ma·ged·don ( Noun )

===Definition===
* '''1.''' The scene of a decisive conflict on a great scale.
* '''2.''' The place where the final battle will be fought between the forces of [[good]] and [[evil]].
* '''3.''' Any great and crucial conflict.

===Etymology===
* [http://wikisource.org/wiki/Bible,_English,_King_James,_Revelation#Chapter_16 Revelations 16:16] (Battlefield of [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mount_Megiddo Megiddo]) "The place of the last battle at the [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Day_of_Judgement Day of Judgement]."

